Uropod (
Fig. 3
) biramous, sympod surface covered with small blunt tubercles irregularly distributed and one blunt small spine in proximal third; sympod with three plumose setae on distolateral margin; exopod 0.04 length of sympod, triangular, endopod half of exopod length, with three short simple apical setae.
